{"tid":1814823,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"退場嘅邏輯，係退一陣又上，而嗰一陣要靜靜雞","createTime":"2020-01-07T05:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T06:06:21.000Z","uid":296931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de54b328d6c3e991b987ebd735e9c80ae55bfaa9","tid":1814823,"uid":296931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"退乜撚嘢場要俾我知，退你老母<br />\n第一隊退完又上無問題，你退一陣開po講fine<br />\n問題係你退完5毛又跟風寫多個po先有問題<br />\n退係可以<br />\n但要留返上嘅可能性<br />\n而且退一陣又上使咩開po放負<br />\n要開po就咪放負，例如講吓你哋點樣上返，俾啲建議仲努力緊嘅我哋，手足唔是condom<br />\n而且<br />\n退一陣要靜靜雞<br />\n唔一定要全人類包括犬隻同維尼熊班𡃁都知<br />\n退一陣時靜靜雞<br />\n咁先可以贏<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁先可以時代革命<br />\n咁先可以光復香港</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f42c62b8ca676970835bf193c3c70092ad2c3f","tid":1814823,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:56:45.000Z","msg":"停止玩膠"},{"pid":"5855e331d002b1448ca55bec7b28176b8e04dd53","tid":1814823,"uid":296931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:06:21.000Z","msg":"個point係如果真係要退唔使話我知，而退一陣係要上"}]}